# How to automate credit assignment on SONA

When making a study on SONA, enter in your study's url (e.g., https://cogtoolslab.org:8881/index.html) 

However, to <i>automate<i> your credit assignment, add the following to the end of your url: `?sona=1&survey_code=%SURVEY_CODE%` (e.g., https://cogtoolslab.org:8881/index.html?sona=1&survey_code=%SURVEY_CODE%)
